data.description: This charming bi-level residence offers comfort, style, and plenty of space for your family. Situated on a large fenced lot, this property boasts numerous features that make it a dream home. The wood laminate floors throughout the first floor provide durability and elegance. The open kitchen is perfect for entertaining, featuring updated cabinets, ample counter space, and all your appliances. Enjoy the convenience of the wrap-around deck accessible directly from the kitchen, extending your living space outdoors. The master bedroom offers a private retreat with its own private entry into the full bath and its own access to the deck, providing a tranquil space to unwind. A finished basement adds additional living space, complete with a laundry area and an unfinished section for storage, allowing for versatility and functionality. Water heater 2006. New electrical box in 2023. Bathroom updated.
